{
  "texts": [
    "In the upcoming version, a user feedback function could be implemented, and validation from experts will be sought to further enhance the platform's capabilities.",
    "Word co-occurrence visualization for contextual analysis.",
    "Texts are entwined with the broader contextual fabric to convey human ideas.",
    "The semantics or referential meaning of a word may undergo changes in different literature, which can be discerned through the distribution of its co-occurring words.",
    "Word cooccurrence refers to the frequency at which different words appear together within a certain context, which is widely applied in word-level cultural studies (Wijaya and Yeniterzi, 2011; Moeller et al., 2018)."
  ]
}